Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.76,0:01:35.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,小櫻的決心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.09,0:01:37.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.80,0:01:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們把他弄到哪兒去了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.50,0:01:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是鳴人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.90,0:01:46.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正不管我怎麼說 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.67,0:01:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也不會相信的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.00,0:01:49.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.95,0:01:52.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不相信佐助已經死了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.80,0:01:53.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.50,0:01:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 佐助還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.20,0:02:02.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會把佐助帶回去的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.90,0:02:05.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾經許諾過
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.90,0:02:07.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.60,0:02:10.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有本事你就來打倒我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.50,0:02:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是以前那個軟弱的我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.10,0:02:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許會告訴你們真相的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.70,0:02:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嵐哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.00,0:02:21.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錯 以前那個嵐早已死了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.30,0:02:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在站在這裏的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.20,0:02:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是被忍法賦予了生命的肉塊罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.40,0:02:43.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻 莎莎美就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.10,0:02:45.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手啊 鳴人 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.31,0:02:46.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別和他戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.37,0:02:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.80,0:02:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他已經不是莎莎美認識的那個溫柔的嵐了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.00,0:02:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地蜘蛛 上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.10,0:03:03.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.70,0:03:05.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莎莎美 對不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.60,0:03:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.10,0:03:22.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.40,0:03:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別過去 小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.20,0:03:31.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神切
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.70,0:03:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後一擊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.20,0:03:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.90,0:03:58.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來…就是你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.50,0:04:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.80,0:04:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好危險 好危險
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.70,0:04:22.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才一大意 差點被幹掉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.50,0:04:26.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得創造了這麼好的奇襲機會
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.90,0:04:29.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻白白浪費了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.20,0:04:30.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.80,0:04:31.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.90,0:04:35.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪你這個拖後腿的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.70,0:04:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拖後腿的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.20,0:04:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.30,0:04:44.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪有…這回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.10,0:04:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這點小傷…根本不算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.30,0:04:55.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,影分身之術
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.90,0:04:58.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然你有三個人 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.34,0:04:59.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就叫五個出來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.60,0:05:16.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神切
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.70,0:05:33.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.10,0:05:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.10,0:05:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好重的傷…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.70,0:05:50.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻…這點小傷…不要緊的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.70,0:05:55.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻 這點小傷不要緊的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.20,0:06:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住口 你再說句看看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.70,0:06:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會再說了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.90,0:06:09.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我要讓它結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.40,0:06:13.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神切 地蜘蛛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.00,0:06:16.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你們的查克拉給我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.34,0:06:37.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.70,0:06:39.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嵐哥哥的招數…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.40,0:06:44.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是風馬一族的歷代首領才會使用的秘術
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.90,0:06:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.40,0:06:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風馬忍法.咒縛曼陀羅
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.30,0:06:54.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.00,0:07:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.10,0:07:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.90,0:07:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.40,0:07:14.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.90,0:07:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.60,0:07:23.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個查克拉牢籠會漸漸縮小
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.70,0:07:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被困在裏邊的人會被碾成細小的碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.10,0:07:31.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要打破它是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.00,0:07:36.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除非我自己解除忍術
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.50,0:07:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.14,0:07:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都做不了…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.10,0:08:01.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什麼都做不了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.70,0:08:08.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.07,0:08:10.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都做不了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.90,0:08:16.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嵐哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.00,0:08:31.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莎莎美…你這混蛋…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.30,0:08:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莎莎美
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.60,0:08:37.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託 醒過來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.20,0:08:42.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變回以前的嵐哥哥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.00,0:08:44.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說過了 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.24,0:08:47.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個嵐已經死了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.30,0:09:05.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嵐哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.50,0:09:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 莎莎美
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.10,0:09:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很想獲得力量
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.30,0:09:18.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再次重振風馬一族
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.88,0:09:22.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道 我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.70,0:09:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 已經可以了 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.02,0:09:28.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.30,0:09:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回村裏去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.30,0:09:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 我現在只是一個怪物了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.70,0:09:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒這回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.90,0:09:39.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好痛苦 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.80,0:09:41.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莎莎美 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.69,0:09:46.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺了…我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.00,0:09:49.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我給…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.80,0:09:56.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你居然打算殺了我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.00,0:09:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嵐哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.60,0:10:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你給我去死
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.30,0:10:21.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.40,0:10:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.40,0:10:27.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先拿你開刀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.60,0:10:31.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莎莎美讓我知道了 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.43,0:10:33.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死並不可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.10,0:10:43.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可怕的是碌碌無為地活著
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.00,0:10:47.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了保護自己珍惜的人而死一點也不可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.50,0:10:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.00,0:10:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管發生了什麼 都不能死
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.40,0:10:57.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.50,0:10:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.60,0:11:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臭小子 你現在還能幹嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.10,0:11:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無謂的掙扎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.40,0:11:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變成碎塊消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.30,0:11:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莎莎美
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.30,0:11:25.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手啊 嵐哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.50,0:11:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莎莎美 你這混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.80,0:11:42.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.60,0:11:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.00,0:11:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.20,0:12:21.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嵐哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.50,0:12:24.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 莎莎美
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.30,0:12:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你留下痛苦的回憶了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.90,0:12:29.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才沒這回事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.10,0:12:33.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留下痛苦回憶的…是嵐哥哥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.90,0:12:38.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我為了哥哥…能做些什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.80,0:12:40.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我該為你做些什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.20,0:12:43.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已經為我做了很多了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.00,0:12:44.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.37,0:12:48.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為莎莎美 我尋回了自我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.30,0:12:56.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.00,0:12:59.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.33,0:13:03.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管為了誰
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.30,0:13:07.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生命都不可以隨便放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.50,0:13:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快跑 小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.00,0:13:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好色仙人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.45,0:13:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來晚了 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.00,0:13:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這邊的情況也不大妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.90,0:13:33.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.29,0:13:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 上來上來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.40,0:13:39.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點 要回地面去了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.80,0:13:49.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莎莎美
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.60,0:13:52.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她不要緊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.20,0:13:54.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是暈過去罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.20,0:13:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.80,0:14:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大蛇丸給我們下了命令
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.80,0:14:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決不能讓你們把佐助帶回木葉村
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.60,0:14:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…佐助他…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.37,0:14:15.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.90,0:14:20.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大蛇丸為了三年後轉生的容器
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.54,0:14:23.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千方百計去保護佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.10,0:14:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嵐…哥哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.10,0:14:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嵐 這裏快崩塌了 趕快過來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.60,0:14:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經是個傀儡了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.00,0:14:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒法活著離開這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.20,0:14:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.00,0:14:53.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.30,0:14:57.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嵐哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.00,0:15:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莎莎美
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.80,0:15:05.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.62,0:15:28.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然你們失去了嵐他們
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.80,0:15:32.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但風馬一族終於逃脫了大蛇丸的魔掌
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.50,0:15:36.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切可以重頭開始了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.70,0:15:39.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定會用嵐哥哥救回的這條命
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.30,0:15:44.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再次復興風馬一族的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.00,0:15:54.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是給你們添了不少麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.20,0:15:56.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莎莎美
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.50,0:16:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半崎 這兩個人就拜託你了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.42,0:16:05.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請您路上當心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.97,0:16:14.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.20,0:16:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 雖然沒能找到佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.50,0:16:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過知道他還在某處活著
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.70,0:16:28.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以確認佐助在成為大蛇丸的容器之前
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.19,0:16:32.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有三年時間
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.09,0:16:34.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣已經很不錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.90,0:16:42.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莎莎美明白了如何為復興一族奮鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.80,0:16:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可我這次只是哭哭啼啼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.70,0:16:49.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是依靠著鳴人 拖他的後腿
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.45,0:16:50.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.90,0:16:54.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也很努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.00,0:16:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我只是在拖後腿
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.80,0:17:01.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己什麼也…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.80,0:17:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說沒這回事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.10,0:17:08.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時小櫻拼命的身影 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.47,0:17:10.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賦予了我勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.70,0:17:16.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是沒有小櫻 我早就被碾碎了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.30,0:17:19.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧小櫻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.60,0:17:21.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.40,0:17:26.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你小子越來越會說話了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.90,0:17:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.50,0:17:31.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不能照顧照顧我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.04,0:17:33.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是身負重傷啊 身負重傷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.20,0:17:35.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.60,0:17:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時 我只是想保護重要的夥伴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.60,0:17:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我來說 現在所能做到的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.90,0:18:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我考慮過了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.30,0:18:01.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.50,0:18:03.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然有著任務等級
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.82,0:18:08.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及小隊成員的種種限制
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.39,0:18:11.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我覺得 無論什麼小隊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.52,0:18:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都應該配備一名醫療忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.45,0:18:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.80,0:18:20.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前在小隊的生存率
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.66,0:18:22.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和任務完成率的報告上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.32,0:18:23.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也寫過同樣的看法
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.47,0:18:27.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是培養醫療忍者並不簡單
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.90,0:18:33.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們需要掌握不同於戰鬥型忍者的技能
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.40,0:18:37.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如極其細微的查克拉控制力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.00,0:18:40.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還必須學習大量的專業知識 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.56,0:18:43.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及將其付諸於實際的頭腦和毅力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.70,0:18:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且要培養一名一流的醫療忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.20,0:18:50.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還需一件重要之物
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.30,0:18:55.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回見了 我現在可是很忙的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.00,0:19:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重要之物…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.34,0:19:05.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又全身纏滿繃帶了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.20,0:19:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣連筷子都拿不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.30,0:19:10.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.50,0:19:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃飯的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.71,0:19:14.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可要溫柔地喂我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.42,0:19:16.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.97,0:19:18.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.30,0:19:26.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起對不起 我開玩笑的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.50,0:19:28.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.40,0:19:36.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然需要些時間
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.10,0:19:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但下次我一定不會繼續拖後腿了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.24,0:19:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.50,0:20:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有事想拜託您
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.95,0:20:05.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.13,0:20:09.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請收我為徒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.40,0:20:33.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來你也很拼命嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.60,0:20:35.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春野櫻 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.28,0:20:38.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽卡卡西說你頭腦清晰
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.30,0:20:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且很有毅力
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.50,0:20:44.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.40,0:20:49.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我可是很嚴格的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.90,0:20:58.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次的任務 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.17,0:21:03.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也並非一無是處啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.20,0:22:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是氣人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.30,0:22:42.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好色仙人那傢伙 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.68,0:22:44.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼收我為徒栽培我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.80,0:22:47.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻都成了綱手婆婆的徒弟 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.06,0:22:48.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在努力修煉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.15,0:22:50.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我卻沒人管
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.50,0:22:52.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.33,0:22:56.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪婆婆給好色仙人指派任務
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.10,0:22:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.15,0:23:01.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就去說她幾句吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.20,0:23:02.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.00,0:23:04.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,監禁機關的三惡人
